[Combining Punishment with Leniency]

37
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:44,760
Li Shaotang, answer me again.

38
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:46,360
Are you a Communist or not?

39
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:47,160
[Are you a Communist or not?]

40
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:52,560
