105
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:30,330
The Cherry Blossom Project.

106
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:32,320
Chief Ohashi would never easily give up

107
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,780
the fruit of his hard work.

108
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,520
So you mean

109
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:36,900
Ohashi's rebuilding of 810 in Myanmar

110
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:38,750
is for his Cherry Blossom Project,

111
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,320
using Chinese prisoners

112
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:42,310
