113
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:44,350
This is a way for them to die in a meaningful way.

114
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:45,480
To die in a meaningful way?

115
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,040
Yes.

116
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:48,230
To die in a meaningful way?

117
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,670
Why don't you let you Japanese people

118
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,070
die in a meaningful way?

119
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,200
Tell me!

120
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:01,260
How far has the Cherry Blossom Project progressed?

121
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,470
Let go of me,

122
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,290
