123
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,630
Let go of me!

124
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:14,850
The Cherry Blossom Project is the highest secret of 810.

125
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:17,970
I don't know the specifics.

126
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:19,570
I only heard that

127
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:21,380
the vaccine and the virus

128
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:23,430
are almost successfully developed.

129
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,390
What virus?

130
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:27,140
I only know its code name.

131
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:31,580
It's KW30.

132
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:34,070
It's used to develop highly contagious

133
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:36,030
and deadly biochemical bombs.

134
00:06:36,050 --> 00:06:38,380
The yellow bombs and the red bombs, right?

135
00:06:40,150 --> 00:06:41,800
The yellow bomb and the red bomb

136
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,130
