137
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:47,450
They've already started being mass produced.

138
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,940
How many of them have been produced?

139
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,340
I don't know.

140
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,380
But

141
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:53,440
I heard that

142
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:55,220
before I left 810,

143
