they had already begun to be transported

144
00:06:56,540 --> 00:06:59,500
to their target locations.

145
00:06:59,530 --> 00:07:01,310
Where are the target locations?

146
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,150
I don't know.

147
00:07:02,180 --> 00:07:03,890
-I'm just a doctor.
-Then what do you know?

148
00:07:03,890 --> 00:07:05,400
I'm just a doctor.

149
00:07:05,470 --> 00:07:06,380
I'm not a biochemical expert.

150
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,670
Where is Ohashi?

151
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:10,770
Section Chief Li, please don't be angry.

152
00:07:10,770 --> 00:07:11,710
When most of us

153
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:13,250
