154
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:15,160
we will experience fluctuations in data

155
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,600
due to some physical

156
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:18,500
and emotional discomfort.

157
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:19,730
That's why we need to

158
00:07:19,730 --> 00:07:21,530
