160
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:25,310
How about this?

161
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,180
Let's take a break.

162
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,810
Get Section Chief Li a glass of water.

163
00:07:30,810 --> 00:07:31,490
