171
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,760
Hurry and inform Vice Captain Feng

172
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,159
about Section Chief Li's situation.

173
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,390
I'll be here keeping an eye on him.

174
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:01,190
Go.

175
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:10,950
Where is 810?

176
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,610
And the target! The location!

177
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:15,030
When we experts and medical staff

178
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:16,510
enter and leave 810,

179
00:08:16,570 --> 00:08:18,200
we are blindfolded

180
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,410
