194
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,800
With poison gas.

195
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,240
You think you are smart!

196
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:21,030
When interrogating Li Shaotang,

197
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,550
