201
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:31,830
So Deputy Chief Xu and I were considering

202
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:33,950
recording what we should record

203
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:35,640
and pretending we didn't hear

204
00:09:35,810 --> 00:09:37,120
what we shouldn't record.

205
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,850
Just record.

206
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:40,000
Write down every word.

207
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,510
If there's any problem with Li Shaotang,

208
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,810
I won't cover for him.

209
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:43,560
Yes.

210
00:09:46,170 --> 00:09:47,040
Wait.

211
00:09:52,230 --> 00:09:54,470
