225
00:10:35,850 --> 00:10:37,900
Lou Mingyuan is not my contact.

226
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:40,410
And I don't have any other contacts.

227
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:43,400
I've said before, I didn't join the Communist Party.

228
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:49,340
[Combining Punishment with Leniency]

229
00:10:47,090 --> 00:10:49,300
