232
00:10:52,690 --> 00:10:54,990
I've said countless times,

233
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:57,260
I did not join the Communist Party in Shanghai.

234
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:59,000
You didn't join the Communist Party in Shanghai.

235
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,030
So did you get inspired

236
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,570
by the Communist Party's ideology

237
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:03,610
during your studies in Tokyo

238
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,870
and join the Communist Party?

239
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,590
Yes or no?

240
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:07,550
Liu,

241
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,710
I have said so many times,

242
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,280
I did not join the Communist Party,

243
00:11:14,170 --> 00:11:16,110
no matter when I was in Shanghai,

244
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:18,050
Japan, or Chongqing.

245
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,400
Section Chief Li,

246
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,250
