248
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:32,590
You joined the Communist Party in Chongqing.

249
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,640
Lou Mingyuan is not your contact;

250
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:37,300
you have another contact, right?

251
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,850
I have said so many times,

252
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,910
I did not join the Communist Party.

253
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:48,030
Since I was born, besides Fengtian,

254
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:49,910
I have only been to Shanghai,

255
00:11:49,930 --> 00:11:51,130
Tokyo, and Chongqing.

256
00:11:51,130 --> 00:11:52,630
That was why I mentioned Chongqing.

257
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,760
It has nothing to do with Lou Mingyuan.

258
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:57,280
