278
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,350
What way?

279
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:44,980
Perhaps...

280
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:47,010
there's a traitor

281
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,120
